====== H7663: שָׂבַר ======

===== Source =====

erroneously   ; (Nehemiah 2:13,15), a primitive root;

===== Meaning =====

to  scrutinize ; by implication (of watching) to  expect  (with hope and patience)

===== Definitions =====

  - scrutinize
  - expect

===== Usage =====

hope, tarry, view, wait.
